PODMAS - still applies to Java

to print something in java is,
System.out.println()
[SYSTEM SHOULD HAVE THE CAPITAL S]

strings can be concatenated,
System.out.println("ABC"+"DEF"+"GHI");

escape characters,
    \\ : \
    \n : new line
    \t : tab

Math.random : gives a random number, and it doesnt require any parameter
    Math.random()

Math.min : gives the least number betwee the limits
    Math.min(1,4) ==> 1

similar for Math.max
    Math.max(1,4) ==> 4


