VARIABLES 

==> integer have a bit storage of 4, just like any other lang

==> we cant name a variable by starting with a number, it cant be a keyword too

==> theres no limit of letters in the name of a variable

primitive data types
    ==> for numbers, byte   short   int   long
                      [8]   [16]    [32]  [64]
    
for float, 32 bits
for double, 64 bits
for char, 16 bits

